<h1 class="headline instapaper_title entry-title" id="stream_title" style="font-size: 50px; line-height: 1.24;" data-remote-headline-edit="title" data-remote-headline-promo-headine="WikiLeaks launches site for Edward Snowden&#x27;s legal defense" data-remote-admin-entry-id="4803237">WikiLeaks launches site for Edward Snowden's legal&nbsp;defense</h1>

  

  

